Chavez Says He’ll Come Out of Recovery Phase in Weeks, Months

-- B y   C h a r l i e   D e v e r e u x
-- 
2011-10-01T16:00:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/chavez-says-he-ll-come-out-of-recovery-phase-in-weeks-months.html
Venezuela ’s President  Hugo Chavez 
said he hopes to come out of his recovery phase after receiving
chemotherapy to treat an unspecified form of cancer in the
coming weeks or months.  Chavez, speaking on state television today, said he’s going
to give a “great surprise” to those who say he’s on the verge
of dying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
